{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hanak, I know him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he-- when it was my turn, I thought, maybe they will give me away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was convinced I am Hamai, I am a student, I am a best friend from, from, Alex.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they knew each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was like a big family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he, he spoke-- before I had the chance to talk anything-- he said, oh, no, I know him, Hamai, he lives-- I think he was a cousin where I was living.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had to show the paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked a it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[GERMAN] Deutsch?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, [GERMAN] Deutsch, [GERMAN] Deutsch, like a typical Slovak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I was dressed like a peasant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[GERMAN] Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the one said to the other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[GERMAN] Deutsch, he said in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He doesn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I, I had to talk Slovak to the head man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was translating it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I knew every word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was my luck, that I had always a little bit of time to think about the answer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he asked me, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What do you make here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I had to give him the same story which I gave to the peasants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I am sick, I am a student.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came here because I need re-convalescence and they are very good to me, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have much time to interrogate me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If he would have been more suspicious, I wouldn't have survived there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because that was really-- what he did, and that is exclusive, he gave a stamp on the, on the identity paper, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means verified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was, for me, a new passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were staying.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
